snippet.title: SNES - Kirby no KiraKira Kids (Part One)
snippet.description: Kirby no KiraKira Kids aka Kirby's Star Stacker is a Japanese-only Super Famicom release. In 1997, the game saw a modified release in the United States on the Game Boy. This video was requested by GameFAQs user Seiichi Omori.
